<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>방문 접수</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/tailwind.min.css">
    <script src="/js/lucide.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 min-h-screen p-6">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-8">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-orange-600">
                    <i data-lucide="user-plus" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">방문 접수 (Walk-in)</h1>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 mt-1">예약 없이 방문한 환자를 즉시 접수합니다.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <form onsubmit="handleSubmit(event)" class="space-y-6">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">환자 성함</label>
                        <div class="relative">
                            <i data-lucide="user" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-slate-400"></i>
                            <input
                                type="text"
                                required
                                class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-orange-500 focus:border-orange-500 outline-none"
                                placeholder="홍길동"
                            />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">연락처</label>
                        <div class="relative">
                            <i data-lucide="phone" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-slate-400"></i>
                            <input
                                type="tel"
                                required
                                class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-orange-500 focus:border-orange-500 outline-none"
                                placeholder="010-1234-5678"
                            />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">이메일 (선택)</label>
                    <div class="relative">
                        <i data-lucide="mail" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-slate-400"></i>
                        <input
                            type="email"
                            class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-orange-500 focus:border-orange-500 outline-none"
                            placeholder="example@email.com"
                        />
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">진료과</label>
                        <select required class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-orange-500 focus:border-orange-500 outline-none bg-white">
                            <option value="">선택해주세요</option>
                            <option value="내과">내과</option>
                            <option value="외과">외과</option>
                            <option value="소아과">소아과</option>
                            <option value="이비인후과">이비인후과</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">전문의</label>
                        <select required class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-orange-500 focus:border-orange-500 outline-none bg-white">
                            <option value="">선택해주세요</option>
                            <option value="김의사 원장">김의사 원장</option>
                            <option value="이의사 과장">이의사 과장</option>
                            <option value="박의사 과장">박의사 과장</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">접수 날짜</label>
                        <div class="relative">
                            <i data-lucide="calendar" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-slate-400"></i>
                            <input
                                type="date"
                                id="dateInput"
                                required
                                class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-orange-500 focus:border-orange-500 outline-none"
                            />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">접수 시간</label>
                        <div class="relative">
                            <i data-lucide="clock" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-slate-400"></i>
                            <input
                                type="time"
                                id="timeInput"
                                required
                                class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-orange-500 focus:border-orange-500 outline-none"
                            />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">증상 및 메모</label>
                    <div class="relative">
                        <i data-lucide="file-text" class="absolute left-3 top-4 w-5 h-5 text-slate-400"></i>
                        <textarea
                            class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-orange-500 focus:border-orange-500 outline-none h-24 resize-none"
                            placeholder="환자의 증상이나 특이사항을 입력하세요."
                        ></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="pt-6 border-t border-slate-200">
                    <button
                        type="submit"
                        class="w-full py-4 bg-orange-600 text-white rounded-xl font-medium text-lg hover:bg-orange-700 transition-colors shadow-sm"
                    >
                        즉시 접수하기
                    </button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/pages/staff-walkin-reception.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
